highlights.text: “Slime You Out (feat. SZA)” by Drake and SZA is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 57 spots at #15.
Drake has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “IDGAF (feat. Yeat)” is the highest at #5.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 349 weeks straight.
“IDGAF (feat. Yeat)” by Drake and Yeat is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #5.
